title: Bring It S01E03 The Wig Is Off WS DSR x264-[NY2] mp4
description:
Original Airdate: March 19, 2014 After getting cheated the week before, the Dancing Dolls return to Memphis looking for payback and are determined to beat one of their biggest rivals, the Prancing Tigerettes. Sunjai learns a hard lesson about what it takes to make the stand battle crew and her mother, Selena, learns a lesson of her own when she tries to bully Dianna. Meanwhile, Camryn gets a chance to perform her very first solo at competition.
